    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, and all electronic features function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and a drive that feels brand new. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example of this model.",
